</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
DEMONSTRATIONS -- CYPRUS; TURKEY -- TERRITORIES AND POSSESSIONS; GREECE -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- TURKEY; CYPRUS -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- GREECE; CYPRUS -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- TURKEY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA072589-0047 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 86463 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 25, 1989, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
