<P>
Photo, (Orange County Edition) COLOR, The Final Trip A truck moves a section of 
the fuselage of United Airlines ill-fated Flight 232 to a hangar in Sioux City, 
Iowa, where it will be inspected for clues to crash cause. Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
