<HEADLINE>
<P>
QUAKE HITS VIRGIN ISLANDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
SAN JUAN, Puerto Rico 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A tremor shook the U.S. Virgin Islands Monday and was felt in neighboring 
Puerto Rico, the Geophysical Institute said. No damage or injuries were 
reported. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
