<TEXT>
<P>
Deputy Chief Named: Ken MacLeod has been named deputy chief of the Orange 
County Fire Department. A 24-year veteran of the department, MacLeod has served 
the last 19 months as assistant director of operations. He spent the preceding 
eight years as assistant director of the administration and support bureaus. 
