HOMOSEXUALS; INVESTIGATIONS; DANNEMEYER, WILLIAM E; HOUSE COMMITTEE ON 
STANDARDS OF OFFICIAL CONDUCT; LEGISLATION -- UNITED STATES; HOUSE OF 
REPRESENTATIVES (U.S.); CONGRESS (U.S.) 
