<TEXT>
<P>
Western Digital Corp., the Irvine computer company, said that Computerland 
Corp. has selected it as a supplier of local area network products. 
</P>
<P>
Western Digital said the products included in the agreement are its EtherCard 
PLUS and TokenCard products. 
</P>
<P>
