<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A headine in Saturday editions stated incorrectly that Interior Secretary 
Manuel Lujan Jr. was being asked by critics to resign from a White House task 
force studying offshore oil drilling. As the accompanying story stated, 
California's two senators and 17 of the state's congressmen are demanding that 
Lujan resign as chairman of the group, not from the group itself. 
</P>
</TEXT>
