<TEXT>
<P>
The government news agency ANGOP claimed today that rebels shot down a military 
transport plane with 48 aboard, killing 42. 
</P>
<P>
Spokesmen for the rebels in Washington and the U.S. State Department said they 
had heard no word of the reported Sunday attack, and the claim could not be 
independently verified. 
